name: Kugelstudie 0014
description:
Geometric study of spherical space, created during a 2006 artist residency at Museumsquartier Wien and Medienturm Graz. Originally shown as a realtime software animation, later used to generate a series of high-resolution still images.

Edition 1/1, 4000x6000px PNG. Marius Watz / @mariuswatz, 2006
